com.newatlanta.appengine.vfs.provider
Class GaeFileContent

java.lang.Object
  com.newatlanta.appengine.vfs.provider.GaeFileContent
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.commons.vfs.FileContent
public class GaeFileContent
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.commons.vfs.FileContent

Implements FileContent for GaeVFS. Differs from the Commons VFS DefaultFileContent in the following ways:

  1. Does not automatically buffer input and output streams.
  2. Allows multiple output streams.

Author:
Vince Bonfanti
